app.use((err, req, res, _next) => {
  console.error(err);
  res.status(500).json({ error: 'Internal Server Error' });
});
```

### 5. `/health` exposes server time (Informational)
`new Date().toISOString()` leaks server clock. Usually harmless, but it's unnecessary information disclosure; some environments strip it.

