| 1 | High | Add `helmet()`, disable `x-powered-by`, add body-size limits |
| 2 | High | Add auth middleware before any route returning user data |
| 3 | High | Add a central error handler that does not leak stacks |
| 4 | Med  | Add rate limiting and request/headers timeouts |
| 5 | Med  | Move port/secrets to env vars; validate at startup |
| 6 | Med  | Add structured logging with header redaction |
| 7 | Low  | Trim `/health` response; decide CORS policy explicitly |
| 8 | Low  | Audit `.env.test` contents & gitignore coverage |

