app.use(express.json({ limit: '100kb' }));
```

### 7. A02: Cryptographic Failures — HTTP only, no TLS (Medium)

`app.listen(3000, ...)` serves plain HTTP. In production this must sit behind a TLS-terminating reverse proxy (nginx, ALB, Cloudflare). If behind a proxy, trust it explicitly so `req.ip` / rate-limit keys are correct:

