Email is PII. Even behind auth, return it only when the caller needs it (e.g. admin role or self-lookup), and never in a list endpoint without explicit purpose.

```js
app.get('/users', requireAuth, (req, res) => {
  const projection = req.user.role === 'admin'
    ? (u) => u
