| 1 | Low–Med  | No security headers (add helmet) |
| 2 | Medium   | `/users` exposes PII without auth |
| 3 | Low      | No rate limiting |
| 4 | Low      | `listen` has no error handler; binds to 0.0.0.0 |
| 5 | Info     | `/health` leaks server time |
| 6 | Info     | No TLS in-process |

