`app.listen(3000)` speaks plain HTTP. That's acceptable **only** if a proxy (nginx / ALB / Cloud Run) terminates TLS in front of it. If so:
- Set `app.set('trust proxy', 1)` (not `true`).
- Enforce HTTPS at the proxy and set HSTS (handled by helmet above).

